<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3925219>
    dc:description "Fig. 1: A Persiscape caspica sp. n., ♀ habitus; B same, ♂ habitus; C Persilena sengleti sp. n., ♀ habitus; D Asiascape parthica sp. n., ♂ habitus; E Gorbiscape gorbachevi sp. n., ♂ habitus; F same, ♀ habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3925219/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3925225>
    dc:description "Fig. 4: Bulb, ventral view. A, B Agelescape cf. livida, from Israel;C Asiascape parthica sp. n.; D Gorbiscape gorbachevi sp. n.; E G. agelenoides. A after Levy (1996), E after de Blauwe (1980), both with modification. Scale bar = 0.2 mm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3925225/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3925227>
    dc:description "Fig. 5: Palps.A Agelescape cf. livida, from Israel, ventral view;B same, retrolateral view; C Gorbiscape gorbachevi sp. n., ventral view; D same, retrolateral view; E Asiascape parthica sp. n., ventral view; F same, retrolateral view. Scale bars = 0.2 mm, if indicated." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3925227/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3925231>
    dc:description "Fig. 7: SEM micrographs of terminal part of bulb, anterior view. A Gorbiscape gorbachevi sp. n.; B Persiscape levyi; C P. ecbatana sp. n. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3925231/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3925245>
    dc:description "Fig. 14: Epigynes. A Gorbiscape gorbachevi sp. n., intact, ventral view; B same, macerated, dorsal view; C, D same, posterior views; E, F Asiascape parthica sp. n., intact, ventral views; G same, macerated, dorsal view; H same, posterior view; I Persilena sengleti sp. n., posterior view; D same, intact, ventral view; K same, antero-ventral view; L same, dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.2 mm. Abbreviation: Cd = copulatory duct." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3925245/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

